Pistol Annies - Hell of a Holiday (Target Exclusive, Vinyl)
description: Hell of a Holiday is the fourth studio and first Christmas album from country music trio Pistol Annies (Miranda Lambert, Ashley Monroe, Angaleena Presley).
Full of new yuletide treats, the project includes 10 festive original tracks written by the Annies with their signature winking humor, while also honoring the spirit of the season.

The title track conjures images of the hectic holiday whirlwind that arrives every Nov. 1, while “Snow Globe” dreams of a romantic winter wonderland. Elsewhere, a family of country-fried characters come to life, and there’s even a new ode to Santa himself.
The project also features their take on standards including “Sleigh Ride,” and Merle Haggard’s “If We Make it Through December,” plus a reimagined “Auld Lang Syne.”

title: Jakks Pacific APEX Legends Wingman Pistol 1:1 Scale Licensed Replica Weapon
description: LOCK N LOAD: Apex Legends fans and collectors alike will love this highly detailed Wingman pistol collectible from the hit video game!
1:1 SCALE: Life-sized, perfect for play and display!
AUTHENTIC DESIGN: Intricately detailed decoration inspired by the in-game weapon. Plastic construction.
FUN FEATURE: Features transformative reload action faithful to the Apex Legends model (no batteries required).
